  "title": "⭐ Urgent Hiring! Junior Brand Ambassador",
  "description": "<p> EVENTS & SALES RECRUITMENT ALERT </p><p>Are you the go-to person for hyping up your crew?</p><p>Can you sell an idea and turn it into an unforgettable experience?</p><p>We’re looking for fresh, driven, and creative minds to join our Events & Sales Team. This is more than just a job — it’s your launchpad into a career where people, energy, and strategy collide.</p><p>Here’s what you’ll be doing:</p><p> Planning and executing events that actually get people talking</p><p> Building real connections with clients, partners & guests</p><p> Driving revenue through smart, people-first sales</p><p> Bringing ideas that make events pop and sales soar</p><p>What we’re looking for:</p><p> Confident communicators who love working with people</p><p> Detail-driven but big-picture thinkers</p><p> You thrive in fast-paced, high-energy settings</p><p> Bonus: experience in events, sales, promotions, or social media</p><p>What’s in it for you:</p><p> Real career growth (not coffee-fetching)</p><p> Learn sales + event strategy from the pros</p><p> A team that works hard and has fun doing it</p><p> [Location]</p><p> Full-time | Entry-level welcome</p><p>This is for the movers, the shakers, and the storytellers.</p><p>If that’s you — apply now, or slide into our DMs with your CV or portfolio. We want to hear from you.</p><p>#EventsJobs #SalesCareers #NowHiring #CreateConnectClose\n\n</p>",
